@Paulo Vitor  Short answer is yes. Panorama appliance uses RTSP protocol to ingest video - so in the config when you add a camera - you would point it to the RTSP URL of the local FLIR Camera.  Based on the Flir specs :
Ethernet/IP, Modbus TCP, TCP, UDP, SNTP, RTSP, RTP, HTTP, ICMP, IGMP, sftp, SMTP, SMB (CIFS), DHCP, MDNS (Bonjour)
